             depos'd, That on the 20th of July, he was at Benjamin's House, from 3 a Clock, till half an Hour past 8 at Night. 
               <persName id="t17240812-32-person158">
                  Mary 
                  Gibson 
               <interp inst="t17240812-32-person158" type="surname" value="Gibson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17240812-32-person158" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17240812-32-person158" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             depos'd, That on the Tuesday Morning Mr. Pargiter came to her House, and told her he was fuddled when he was robb'd. Ann Miller depos'd, That she lodg'd in Benjamin Brightwell's House, and that he was there at work till half an Hour past 9 a Clock at Night, the 20th of July. 
               <persName id="t17240812-32-person159">
                  Susan 
                  Tailor 
