             depos'd, she saw Benjamin Brightwell, at her Stable Door, between 9 and 10 a Clock at Night, and talk'd to him there, and he was going to lye at Mr. Lomax's House. 
               <persName id="t17240812-32-person160">
                  Thomas 
                  Taylor 
